Package org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.execution.search.extractor

Class FieldHitExtractor

java.lang.Object
org.elasticsearch.xpack.ql.execution.search.extractor.AbstractFieldHitExtractor
org.elasticsearch.xpack.sql.execution.search.extractor.FieldHitExtractor
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.elasticsearch.common.io.stream.NamedWriteable, org.elasticsearch.common.io.stream.Writeable, HitExtractor
public class FieldHitExtractor extends AbstractFieldHitExtractor
Extractor for ES fields. Works for both 'normal' fields but also nested ones (which require hitName to be set). The latter is used as metadata in assembling the results in the tabular response.
